<% layout('layout/boilerplate') %>

  <!-- About Section -->
  <section id="about" class="bg-light py-5">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row align-items-center">
        <!-- Image Section -->
        <div class="col-md-6 mb-4 mb-md-0">
          <div class="image-container">
            <img
              src="https://th.bing.com/th?id=OIP.tnPVvQ8pSseQsOlgTj9IdQHaGa&w=268&h=232&c=8&rs=1&qlt=90&o=6&dpr=1.5&pid=3.1&rm=2"
              alt="About ecoBuddy" class="img-fluid rounded about-img wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.3s">
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Text Section -->
        <div class="col-md-6 text-center text-md-start">
          <h2 class="text-success fw-bold mb-3 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.3s">About ecoBuddy</h2>
          <p class="mb-4 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.6s">
            ecoBuddy is your trusted platform for finding eco-friendly facilities and resources, including recycling
            bins, EV charging stations, and eco-conscious businesses. We are dedicated to making sustainability
            accessible and empowering communities to make eco-friendly choices with ease.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-unstyled">
            <li class="wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.9s"><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success me-2"></i>Locate
              eco-friendly facilities near you</li>
            <li class="wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="1.2s"><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success me-2"></i>Access
              real-time updates on facility availability</li>
            <li class="wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="1.5s"><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success me-2"></i>Promote
              sustainable living in your community</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-success mt-4 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="1.8s">Get in Touch</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Enhanced Mission Section -->
      <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="col-12 text-center">
          <h3 class="text-primary fw-bold mb-3 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.3s">Our Mission</h3>
          <p class="lead wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.6s">
            At ecoBuddy, our mission is to pave the way for a sustainable future by empowering individuals and
            businesses
            to adopt eco-friendly practices. We believe that small, consistent actions collectively lead to meaningful
            environmental change. Our platform connects people with accessible, real-time information about eco-friendly
            facilities, products, and services. We aim to create a world where sustainability is ingrained in everyday
            life,
            making it effortless for everyone to contribute to a greener planet.
          </p>
          <p class="wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.9s">
            ecoBuddy is driven by a deep commitment to reducing carbon footprints, minimizing waste, and promoting
            renewable resources. Our approach is rooted in the belief that by fostering a community of like-minded
            individuals and businesses, we can build a resilient, eco-conscious society that protects our planet for
            generations to come.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-unstyled mt-4">
            <li class="wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="1.2s"><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success me-2"></i>Make
              sustainability easy and accessible for all</li>
            <li class="wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="1.5s"><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success me-2"></i>Provide
              real-time data to support informed decisions</li>
            <li class="wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="1.8s"><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success me-2"></i>Foster
              environmental awareness through community engagement</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-success mt-4 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="2.1s">Join Our Mission</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Community Engagement Section -->
      <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="col-12 text-center">
          <h3 class="text-primary fw-bold mb-3 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.3s">Engage with Us</h3>
          <p class="lead wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.6s">
            Sustainability is not a one-person job – it’s a collective effort. At ecoBuddy, we strive to create
            a vibrant community of eco-conscious individuals and businesses who are passionate about reducing their
            environmental impact. By joining ecoBuddy, you’re not just finding eco-friendly facilities, you’re
            also becoming part of a larger movement to promote green practices, inspire change, and build a sustainable
            future.
          </p>
          <p class="wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.9s">
            Whether you're a business looking to contribute to sustainability, an individual eager to reduce your
            carbon footprint, or someone simply seeking information on eco-friendly options, ecoBuddy offers
            the tools and resources you need to make a lasting difference.
          </p>
          <div class="wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="1.2s">
            <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-success mt-4" style="background-color: #00a859; border: none;">Get
              Involved</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Community Impact Section -->
      <div class="row mt-5" style="background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 40px 20px;">
        <div class="col-12 text-center">
          <h3 class="fw-bold mb-4 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.3s">Our Impact in Action</h3>
          <p class="lead wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.6s">
            ecoBuddy is more than just a platform—it's a catalyst for change. By fostering a community of eco-conscious
            individuals and businesses, we're not just promoting sustainability—we're creating a lasting impact.
          </p>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.9s">
              <div class="impact-box p-4 bg-success text-white rounded shadow-lg"
                style="box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 167, 89, 0.3);">
                <h4 class="fw-bold">Empowering Green Businesses</h4>
                <p>We've partnered with local eco-friendly businesses to help them thrive in a sustainable economy. Your
                  participation supports green business growth.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="1.2s">
              <div class="impact-box p-4 bg-success text-white rounded shadow-lg"
                style="box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 167, 89, 0.3);">
                <h4 class="fw-bold">Reducing Carbon Footprints</h4>
                <p>Our community's collective eco-friendly actions help reduce carbon emissions, one sustainable choice
                  at a time. Every step makes a difference.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="1.5s">
              <div class="impact-box p-4 bg-success text-white rounded shadow-lg"
                style="box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 167, 89, 0.3);">
                <h4 class="fw-bold">Building Awareness for Future Generations</h4>
                <p>Through community programs, ecoBuddy is helping to educate the next generation on sustainable living
                  and green practices that will protect our planet.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="1.8s">
            Join us in making a difference—together we can create a sustainable future for everyone.
          </p>
          <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-light mt-4 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="2.1s"
            style="background-color: #23ef10; border: none;">Become Part of the Impact</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>